name: Shell Corena S3 RX 46

localDocs.name: Corena S3 RX 46 (2017) United Kingdom EN 140002340634 EHS V1.8 13-JUN-2023

marketing: Shell Corena S3 RX is a premium quality synthesized air compressor oil, based on Shell’s advanced Gas-to-Liquids (GTL) base oil technology combined with an advanced performance additive system. It is designed to provide excellent protection and performance for compressors running with oil change intervals of 6,000 hours and up to 8,000 hours under certain conditions.
